author: ehu
msg: Fix issue #2411: Merge requires access to '.' when adding files.
(create_empty_file): Remove the assumption that have_write_lock applies to
the current working directory. Create a temporary file in the adm_access
tmp directory if we have a write lock, use a system temp dir otherwise.
(apply_text_delta): Find the adm_access closest to the file we're
receiving a delta for and pass that to create_empty_file().
